item.title: Research in Additive Manufacturing at EML
item.description: In the summer of 2022, I attended the “Young Engineers’ Experience” program hosted by the Experimental Mechanics Laboratory (EML) at San Diego State University (SDSU). Under the mentorship of Dr. George Youssef and EML, this experience opened my eyes to a completely different side of mechanical engineering and piqued my interest in the field of additive manufacturing.
